<plot>A security camera at a high-end coffee shop catches an encounter between a women customer and a pudgy, aproned barista. In grainy black and white, we see and hear her order a cappuccino, but not just any cappuccino: a decaf, double shot, extra hot, extra dry, with no sugar and no chocolate. And when she asks for non-fat milk, the barista unleashes a pent up fury. Will she survive to enjoy her drink?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?400074</url></doc>
